### Problem14

Look at the following code:

```java
int b = 648;
int a = 32;
int c = 0;
while (b > 0) {
    if (b % 2 == 1) c = c + a;
    b = b >> 1;
    a = a << 1;
}
```

 The value of c is _____(0)\___ after executing the program (Hint: Try some simple numbers, and find the relationship of c between a and b. Figure out the nature of this code).
